trans-unit.source: Provides a component editor for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItemCollection"></xref> objects in a control that is derived from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListControl"></xref> or a similar control.
trans-unit.target: Gir et komponent redigeringsprogram for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItemCollection"> </xref> objekter i en kontroll som er avledet av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListControl"> </xref> eller lignende kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The ListItemsCollectionEditor class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItem> elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItemCollection> object within a control that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListControl> or a similar control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ListItemsCollectionEditor gir et brukergrensesnitt for redigering av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItem>elementer i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItemCollection>objekt i en kontroll som er avledet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListControl>eller lignende kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItem>

trans-unit.source: The ListItemsCollectionEditor is invoked by selecting the ellipsis (**…**) button on the **ListItems** property in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer.
trans-unit.target: ListItemsCollectionEditor aktiveres ved å velge ellipsen (**... **)-knappen på den **ListItems** egenskap i den **Egenskaper** rutenett med den visuelle utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A> method always returns `false` to indicate that only one object can be selected at a time in the editor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>metoden returnerer alltid `false` til å angi at bare ett objekt kan velges om gangen i redigeringsprogrammet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor.HelpTopic%2A> property returns the name of the Help topic that the editor displays.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor.HelpTopic%2A>egenskapen returnerer navnet på hjelpeemnet som viser redigeringsprogrammet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor.HelpTopic%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor> class when you select the ellipsis (**…**) button on the **ListItems** property in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer, when designing a control that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListControl> class or other control that encapsulates a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItemCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av klassen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor>Når du velger ellipsen (**... **)-knappen på den **ListItems** egenskap i den **Egenskaper** rutenett med den visuelle utformeren når du utformer en kontroll som er avledet av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListControl>klasse eller en annen kontroll innkapsler en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItemCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListControl> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the collection to edit.
Gets a value indicating whether multiple <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItem"></xref> elements can be selected at one time.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om flere <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItem"> </xref> elementer kan velges om gangen.

trans-unit.source: The CanSelectMultipleInstances method always returns `false`; thus, only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItem> object can be selected at a time in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CanSelectMultipleInstances returnerer alltid `false`; derfor bare én <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItem>objekt kan velges om gangen i den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListItem>

trans-unit.source: Gets the Help topic to display for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter hjelpeemnet skal vises for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The HelpTopic property gets the name of the Help topic to display when the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor> dialog box **Help** button is clicked or when the **F1** key is pressed.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen HelpTopic henter navnet på hjelpeemnet skal vises når det <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor>dialogboksen **hjelpe** -knappen eller når den **F1** tast.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ListItemsCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that specifies the Help topic to display.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som angir hjelpeemnet for å vise.</xref:System.String>
